## 4. Receipt store & privacy

Retrieval by receipt-id + lookup token (or token alone) — never raw principal/`record_id`. Stored
fields hold hashes (`record_id_hash`, `lookup_token_hash`) plus `receipt_id`, CBOR/JSON, schema +
protocol + source versions, `user_canister_id`, `issued_at`, scope + residual-disclosure metadata.
Idempotent by `receipt_id`. Private/token-gated, not publicly enumerable.

