## 5. Disclosure scope (DRAFT — pending O2)

**Erased (user canister):** direct-chat messages, bio, avatar, profile background, contacts, blocked
users, saved crypto accounts, BTC/one-sec addresses, PIN, unique-person proof, wallet config, local
username/display_name copies.
**Remains:** `user_index` deletion tuple (maps removed); `identity` link nulled (auth-record
persistence **O2**); group/community membership removed (authored-message persistence **O2**);
storage/online/notifications/email-auth out of scope (**O2**); empty user-canister shell; hashed
receipt metadata (token-gated). Build wording on `RESIDUAL_TRUST_STATEMENT.md`.

